title: Kill Bill and Star Wars get married
description:
George Lucas & Quentin Tarantino get married: This is the visual result. This started
out of my own curiosity about Star Wars special effects when I was a teen and tried to do this myself on 8mm film using Xacto blades and colored ink markers. I stumbled upon "LSmaker 0.967beta" last year. So I figured what the hell, give it a try.

Note project is incomplete, as it takes over a week to do 30 seconds of this.
It has been removed several times from Vimeo and Youtube. Not many people have 
seen this. Check back in a year to see if the file has added special effects. The
audio is complete and will not be changed further. The portion where there are 40+ lightsabers in use at one time is why this project has stopped. I can only do up to 10 layers, not 40. 



ENJOY; a 53 year old crippled Star Wars geek who learned how to do Rotoscoping
